Class TeVirtualMIDI

  • java.lang.Object
    • TeVirtualMIDI

  • public class TeVirtualMIDI
extends java.lang.Object
    Loads a system library teVirtualMidi.dll and constructs a virtual MIDI port with the name given to the constructor.
    Author:
    Tobias Erichsen
